relation: Gfx sending in a chat window
textBeforeTable: AmiGG - Implemented features of the protocols Antispam stopping most of chain messages and similar. Displaying pictures of a person you talk to. Detailed preferences giving you a possibility to highly customize the way AmiGG looks and works. Pop3 module checking for new e-mails on your account. Files and images sending (quite self-explaining ;-). Animated emoticons - normal thing in modern messengers, still new features in Amiga programmes.. Sauronizator plug-in tracing a person you talk to. You can check IP, messenger version etc. AmigaAMP plug-in changing current status
textAfterTable: AmiGG - Requirements 1. Minimum hardware requirements:   Classic Amiga : AmigaOS3.0+, MUI3.8, 8 MB Fast, 68020+   MorphOS   AmigaOS 4.0   AROS: Processor x86 2. Required MUI classes: TextInput.mcc +28, TextEditor.mcc +15 (included), NList.mcc +20, + NFloattext.mcc + NListview.mcc Busy.mcc +17, Toolbar.mcc +15, 3. Other requirements: - wbstart.library +2 for "internet update" option
